metadata.name: Fist of the Unlimited Hand
metadata.description: 1000 editions of the Unlimited Hand, representing 1000 copies of the album Fist of the Unlimited Hand by artist FALCOhereimfine. This GIF image represents ownership of 5 songs (digital copies) and rights to possible perks within the sphere of FALCO. Your support would mean the pressing of vinyl records, merchandise, and touring. Thank you to anyone and everyone who participates in my music.  - FALCO
